    User Request (Natural Language Query)
                    ↓
    Frontend (Next.js) → Chat UI · query input · results table
                    |
                    | (HTTP/REST)
                    ↓
    Backend Spring Server → Prompt builder · response parser · API router
                    |
                    | (Ollama API)
                    ↓
    Ollama LLM (qwen2.5-coder) → SQL generation · schema-aware reasoning
                    |
                    | (MCP protocol)
                    ↓
